Description: This has been one of my favorite guitars with a sound perfect for blues, rock and country coming from the 2 MP-90 single coil pickups. I have too many guitars and have decided to sell all but the ones that have sentimental value. Description:From country twang to blues-rock bite, Fender's Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe electric guitar gives you the expression and tone you've always wanted. Like the rest of the Modern Player Series, the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe features a comfortable C-shaped neck. Its chambered mahogany body and string-through-body Stratocaster bridge give you epic sustain and a fat, woody sound. But the crowning glory of the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe is its pair of classic-style MP-90 single-coil pickups. Fender Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe Semi-hollowbody Electric Guitar at a Glance: The bite and growl of P-90-style pickupsResonant chambered mahogany bodyRock-solid Strat-style bridge The bite and growl of P-90-style pickups Nothing beats the crunch and growl of classic P-90-style pickups. That's why Fender gave their Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe a pair of their custom MP-90 single-coils. These pickups let the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe singe the blues and tear out gritty rock riffs with ease. Discover the tone that's been shaping modern music for decades with the Fender Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe! Resonant chambered mahogany body Not only does the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe's chambered mahogany body make this an incredibly comfortable guitar to play, but it also adds depth and resonance to its tone. Fat, warm, and woody, the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe goes beyond the classic tone of a Fender Telecaster. Rock-solid Strat-style bridge To top it all off, Fender decided to give the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe a modern Stratocaster bridge. This bridge features a 6-saddle hardtail configuration, which lets you perfectly tune your axe. Even cooler, the Modern Player Telecaster Thinline Deluxe gives you the extra-tight sonics of a string-through-body tailpiece, providing you with tons of extra sustain.
